-- S. Africa May Consider ‘Use It Or Lose It’ Mine Rights Approach
-- B y   A n t o n y   S g u a z z i n
-- 2011-02-08T06:12:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-08/south-africa-says-may-consider-use-it-or-lose-it-approach-to-mine-rights.html
  South Africa ’s Mines Minister Susan
Shabangu said she may consider “a use it or lose it” approach
to mine exploration rights because of inadequate exploration
despite the issue of a large number of rights.  Shabangu spoke at the Mining Indaba conference in  Cape Town 
today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
